infra.name: te0808_9eg_1e
infra.display: UltraSOM (ZYNQ-UltraScale+) TE0808-9EG-1E(A: 2GB DDR). SPRT PCB: REV04.
infra.description: Zynq UltraScale+ TE0808-9EG-1E(A: 2GB DDR) Board (form factor 5.2x7.6 cm) with 4x 512 MByte DDR4, speed grade -1 and extended temperature range. Board Part is only with minimum PS-Setup. Use for own carrier or simple SDK debugging. User must configure B2B MIOs manually, depending on his carrier board connection. Without user PS configuration only JTAG and QSPI boot is possible with this board part file.
infra.author: trenz.biz
